sources.title: Swamp Shark | Full Action Adventure Movie
sources.description:
Swamp Shark - An animal smuggling ring accidentally releases a deadly shark into the swamplands of Atchafalaya Basin causing carnage to the residents and visitors to the upcoming Gator Fest.
2011.  Stars: Christopher Berry, Wade Boggs, Marcus Lyle Brown
